cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL

This paper deals with the task of object detection in fashion photos on social media, which is a computer vision problem. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of unsupervised learning, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia). The paper also deals with the problem of large amounts of unlabeled data, which could fall under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) or cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper deals with fashion trends, which could involve natural language processing and sentiment analysis, falling under cs.CL (Computation and Language).
